{"tid":1967994,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"德田街市海鮮檔遇竊　失約兩萬元硬幣","createTime":"2020-04-11T10:32:02.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-11T11:47:14.000Z","uid":3090,"like":2,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"9844cfc3a4a8b3d146aa23c3e242992284f9e292","tid":1967994,"uid":3090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-11T10:32:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1dU8Ryr.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1dU8Ryr.jpg&h=94c89381&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n檔主黃先生(藍衣)表示昨日收檔時未有收好硬幣。(張開裕攝)<br />\n<br />\n藍田德田街市內一海鮮檔，今晨(11日)9時45分，檔主返回營業期間，發現一個用作存放硬幣的膠桶空空如也，原本裝有的約兩萬港元硬幣懷疑被人偷走，於是報警，警方接報到場調查，案件列作盜竊，暫未有人被捕。<br />\n<br />\n據姓黃檔主指，自己經營海鮮生意約40年，估計昨日收工時忘記將該個膠桶放回店內，有途經人士見到一大桶硬幣放在路邊而起貪念，惜店舖的閉路電視日前損毀未有重新安裝，未有拍下案發過程。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20200411/mobile/bkn-20200411101132027-0411_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20200411%2Fmobile%2Fbkn-20200411101132027-0411_00822_001.html&d=PwmYTnxQQ9jzt6ozq479VfUf%2F0pSCBsIIvLsnv1ZXiY%3D&h=69dbdd0b\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20200411/mobile/bkn-20200411101132027-0411_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"e21ef09c7453f1e051002f4d3a49e6354cfa14cc","tid":1967994,"uid":249885,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-11T10:35:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://gifrun.com/programs/temp/49cdbfa1074649a1b364074cc822cf21.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgifrun.com%2Fprograms%2Ftemp%2F49cdbfa1074649a1b364074cc822cf21.gif&h=2b0c7240&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e74107819c7e767baba538e947da456ec9e97ac5","tid":1967994,"uid":215734,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-11T10:41:20.000Z","msg":"應該都幾撚重<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"165e25d633f06fe1ee2cca5f34a3979add64953f","tid":1967994,"uid":307203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyT